<section id="about" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About smartEdu</h2>
    <div class="section-content">
      <p>smartEdu is a leading school management solution that helps educational institutions streamline their administrative processes, enhance communication, and improve overall efficiency. With smartEdu, schools can effectively manage student data, track academic progress, handle admissions and enrollments, facilitate teacher-student communication, and much more.</p>
