          <p>Efficiently manage student information, attendance, grades, and academic records.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Teacher Collaboration</h4>
          <p>Facilitate communication and collaboration among teachers, parents, and students.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Admissions & Enrollment</h4>
          <p>Simplify the admissions and enrollment process with online forms and automated workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Class Scheduling</h4>
          <p>Create and manage class schedules, assign teachers, and allocate resources efficiently.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Exam & Grade Management</h4>
          <p>Streamline exam creation, grading, and result management for efficient assessment processes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h4>Parent Portal</h4>
          <p>Provide parents with secure access to their child's academic information and progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

